title: Baxton Studio OMY-161-J001 Storage-Ottomans, 18Lx47Wx16.5H, Espresso Brown
features: Full leather with durable pu-coated upholstery
Lift-top lid with child safe hinges
description: Perfect for the foot of your bed or an entryway, this convenient storage bench offers sturdy, dependable seating. Additionally, spacious storage space is revealed when the top lid is lifted. Safety hinges prevent the lid from slamming shut. Stash away shoes and umbrellas for an entryway bench or extra pillows and blankets when used as a trunk at the end of your bed. The surfaces are lightly padded and then upholstered in durable dark brown bycast leather. The feet are black wood and include non-marking feet to protect your flooring Luxurious and classic, leather furniture can be as formal or as casual as the dcor demands. Showcase it in an urban loft and it's oh-so-chic, or nestle it in a family den and it becomes invitingly cozy. Plus, today's upholstery leather is quite user-friendly-protective finishing gives it greater durability for long-term performance, and a quick swipe with a damp cloth takes care of most daily dirt and spills. For elegant accents of leather, Baxton Furniture Studios presents its extensive line of ottomans and benches. This square storage ottoman features a high-density foam cushion and solid-wood frame wrapped in full Bycast leather. Flip open the seat (with the help of interior metal hinges) and the finished interior serves as a deep, open storage area. Low, angled feet also provide steady support and complement the ottoman's clean, versatile style. Available in Black or Espresso Brown, this piece adeptly combines good looks with space efficiency. -Kara Karll
